Description: Bank Aljazira is a public company, listed on Saudi Stock Exchange “Tadawul” (TDWL) since January 1993. It operates within the Banks sector focusing on Diversified Banks. It has companies operating across Saudi Arabia, working on Multi-line Insurance, Investment Banking and Brokerage, Diversified Capital Markets and Specialized Finance. Bank Al Jazira is based in Jeddah, Saudi Arabia and was established in October 1976.
